        <para>The contributed toolbox "quapro" may also be of interest, in
            particular for singular <literal>Q</literal>.
        </para>
    </refsection>
    <refsection>
        <title>Memory requirements</title>
        <para>Let r be</para>
        <programlisting>
            r=min(m,n)
        </programlisting>
        <para>Then the memory required by qp_solve during the computations
            is
        </para>
        <programlisting>
            2*n+r*(r+5)/2 + 2*m +1
        </programlisting>
    </refsection>
